        </entry>
        <entry xml:id="CattleandSheep_ArnolAMacPhailandNCampbellcattle-d0e130">
          <form>
            <orth>taghanach</orth>
          </form>
          <def>[bò] a chaidh seach laogh tri tuiris ach tha bainne aige or aiche.</def>
        </entry>
        <entry xml:id="CattleandSheep_ArnolAMacPhailandNCampbellcattle-d0e139">
          <form>
            <orth>gamhnach</orth>
          </form>
          <def>bò chaidh seach laogh ach aig am bheil bainne s tha am bainne blasta.</def>
        </entry>
        <entry xml:id="CattleandSheep_ArnolAMacPhailandNCampbellcattle-d0e148">
          <form>
            <orth>sealbhach</orth>
          </form>
          <def>bò air ùr-breith.</def>
        </entry>
        <entry xml:id="CattleandSheep_ArnolAMacPhailandNCampbellcattle-d0e157">
          <form>
            <orth>seadhanach</orth>
          </form>
          <def>bò tri bliadhna le bainne gun laogh.</def>
        </entry>
      </div>
